<body>
<section id="description">
</section>
<ol id="conformance">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/Participant2.html">CDA Participant2</xref></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>@typeCode</tt> = "SBJ"</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>awarenessCode</tt></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> satisfy: Patient awareness SHALL contain exactly one participant / participantRole / id, which SHALL have exactly one value, which SHALL also be present in ClinicalDocument / recordTarget / patientRole / id.</li>
</ol>
<ol id="aggregate">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.hl7.rim.doc/classes/InfrastructureRoot.html">RIM Infrastructure Root</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.hl7.rim.doc/classes/Participation.html">RIM Participation</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/Participant2.html">CDA Participant2</xref></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>@typeCode</tt> = "SBJ"</li>
<li>[CCD] <b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>awarenessCode</tt></li>
<li>[CCD] <b>SHALL</b> satisfy: Patient awareness SHALL contain exactly one participant / participantRole / id, which SHALL have exactly one value, which SHALL also be present in ClinicalDocument / recordTarget / patientRole / id.</li>
</ol>
